org.puredata.core

Interface PdReceiver

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    PdDispatcher, PdReceiver.Adapter, PureDataP5Base

    public interface PdReceiver
    PdReceiver is an interface for printing and receiving messages from Pd, to be used with setReceiver in PdBase.
    Author:
    Peter Brinkmann (peter.brinkmann@gmail.com)

    • Nested Class Summary

      Nested Classes 
      Modifier and Type Interface and Description
      static class  PdReceiver.Adapter
      Adapter for PdReceiver implementations that only need to handle a subset of Pd messages
